item.title: Need help portforwarding!
item.dc:creator: @TeleNubby TeleNubby
item.description:
@TeleNubby wrote:

Try going to http://www.portforward.com

Click on Port-Forward at the top. Then click on the brand of your Router, then click on it’s model. It will give you full instructions on how to port-forward ( dont worry about which game to pick, just pick the 1st one. You can change the port they tell you, by simply putting in the port you want to port forward instead. )
